ilidar-api-py is a software driver for iLidar-ToF. It includes example
projects that uses: OpenCV. Therefore, open source libraries are used
in the example projects.

All software licenses used in the development of ilidar-api-py are announced
as follows(The license of ilidar-api-py is also mentioned):

